file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: JILA API V1
  version: v1
paths:
  "/api/sync/categories":
    get:
      summary: categories sync
      tags:
      - Categories
      parameters:
      - name: last_sync
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                categories:
                - id: 1
                  name: common phrases
                  images:
                    thumbnail: 
                    normal: 
                  games:
                    image: false
                    audio: false
  "/api/sync/entries":
    get:
      summary: entries sync
      tags:
      - Entries
      parameters:
      - name: last_sync
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                entries:
                - id: 1
                  description: description
                  entry_word: Jalangardi
                  pronunciation: 
                  word_type: noun
                  meaning: Goanna
                  example: 
                  example_translation: 
                  alternate_translations:
                  - Sand Monitor
                  alternate_spellings:
                  - alternate spelling 1
                  audio: 
                  images:
                    thumbnail: 
                    normal: 
                  categories:
                  - 1
  "/api/sync/image_credits":
    get:
      summary: image_credits sync
      tags:
      - Image Credits
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                image_credits:
                - attribution_text: Saltwater Crocodile - MR Jordan Woodside - CC
                    BY-SA 3.0
                  link: http://link.to.image.png
  "/api/sync/all":
    get:
      summary: all sync
      tags:
      - All
      parameters:
      - name: last_sync
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                categories:
                - id: 1
                  name: common phrases
                  images:
                    thumbnail: 
                    normal: 
                  games:
                    image: false
                    audio: false
                entries:
                - id: 1
                  description: description
                  entry_word: Jalangardi
                  pronunciation: 
                  word_type: noun
                  meaning: Goanna
                  example: 
                  example_translation: 
                  alternate_translations:
                  - Sand Monitor
                  alternate_spellings:
                  - alternate spelling 1
                  audio: 
                  images:
                    thumbnail: 
                    normal: 
                  categories:
                  - 1
                image_credits:
                - attribution_text: Saltwater Crocodile - MR Jordan Woodside - CC
                    BY-SA 3.0
                  link: http://link.to.image.png
servers:
- url: http://{defaultHost}
  variables:
    defaultHost:
      default: jila.herokuapp.com
